==English==

===Etymology===
Ultimately from the {{etyl|la|en}} term {{m|la|āridus||dry, arid, parched}}, confer its synonymous contracted form {{term|ardus|lang=la}}. Originally from the verb {{m|la|āreo||I am dry, I am parched}}, akin to {{m|la|ārdeō||I'm on fire, I burn}}.

